{"tid":1925677,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"荷李活影視業陷停工潮","createTime":"2020-03-14T14:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T14:17:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38de18fec62acbd3cc1f75631a2e6f041c92a7aa","tid":1925677,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200313/PYLEBTLQG553247TBJ3NSKGWYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200313%2FPYLEBTLQG553247TBJ3NSKGWYE%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=c523e3cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200313%2FPYLEBTLQG553247TBJ3NSKGWYE%2F&h=d4763fb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200313/PYLEBTLQG553247TBJ3NSKGWYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n荷李活影視業陷停工潮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200313/large/1584020153_13be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200313%2Flarge%2F1584020153_13be.jpg&h=fd3183ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巨星湯告魯斯主演之《職業特工隊7》於意大利威尼斯的拍攝已取消。劇照<br />\n<br />\n近日荷李活影視界均受疫情影響，當中湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise）原定於上月20日飛抵意大利威尼斯，拍攝主演的《職業特工隊7》，但由於意大利爆發疫症，靚佬湯一度滯留於酒店之中，幸劇組當中未有人受到感染。電影公司表示，他們應當地政府要求暫停公眾聚會，更改為期三個星期的大型拍攝計劃。該片原定於明年暑假檔期上映，外界估計將會延期上映。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【兩屆影帝】獲奧巴馬頒授勳銜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200313/large/1584020152_7781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200313%2Flarge%2F1584020152_7781.jpg&h=f7e906c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇集《The Falcon and the Winter Soldier》取消於布拉格的取景。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200313/large/1584020152_4cb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200313%2Flarge%2F1584020152_4cb3.jpg&h=7bad8a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFox科幻新劇《neXt》有工作人員確診，令拍攝進度受阻。劇照<br />\n<br />\n另外，Marvel劇集《The Falcon and the Winter Soldier》最近亦受疫情影響，取消在捷克首都布拉格的外景拍攝，攝製隊要返美國等待進一步安排，而Fox科幻新劇《neXt》的其中一名50多歲女工作人員，日前確診感染了武漢肺炎。而近日荷李活的訪問與電影宣傳活動，都接連取消，或只作網上直播宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：仰華"}]}